dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Shows interstate highways and other superhighways, national monuments, points of interest, elevations in feet, ferries, toll bridges, capitals, cities, towns, metropolitan areas, national parks, national forests, state lines, international boundaries, and time zone boundaries. Includes list of toll roads, mileage chart, and text describing points of interest. Includes 4 insets: Metropolitan New York -- Washington D.C.-- Eastern Canada -- Miami
